seo_description:
A woman’s life unravels when her sister steals her identity after a passionate one‑night stand with a powerful CEO — six years later, she’s hired as his legal advisor, reigniting their chemistry.
As their bond deepens, her sister’s desperate sabotage schemes escalate — until a shocking revelation exposes buried secrets, reuniting a fractured family and giving the couple the second chance they never knew they needed.
